{"tid":2291512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肺炎好恐怖 中左唔死一身孱 好快無抗體又有後遺症","createTime":"2020-11-19T00:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T13:18:42.000Z","uid":78016,"like":9,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7a32e429577382e1e61fbab8bb4b54546aa33f4a","tid":2291512,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:05:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://health.mingpao.com/新冠肺炎-康復者身上收集恢復血漿-6成人康復/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.mingpao.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%E8%80%85%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E8%A1%80%E6%BC%BF-6%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%2F&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5sFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=8b729f0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.mingpao.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%E8%80%85%E8%BA%AB%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E8%A1%80%E6%BC%BF-6%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%BA%B7%E5%BE%A9%2F&h=cc70ca69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.mingpao.com/新冠肺炎-康復者身上收集恢復血漿-6成人康復/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄:<br />\n港大醫學院內科學系臨牀教授、瑪麗醫院內科榮譽顧問醫生孔繁毅表示，。。。。。。孔說這情况因人而異，「有些人的<span class=\"red\">抗體水平3個月間都無下降過</span>，有些人卻跌得快，視乎年紀、健康狀况和有否服藥，年輕人的抗體一般維持得更久」。<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院<span class=\"red\">400多個覆診病人中，約30人有後遺症</span>，部分人味覺和嗅覺未完全恢復，5人肺有纖維化，主要是曾接受深切治療的嚴重肺炎病人，當中2人已於3個月後完全康復；另有病人剛出院時行樓梯只能行半層樓，幾個月後進步至可行2層樓。他估計，七八成有肺部後遺症者肺功能於一年後完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n400人得30個有後遺症<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">有</span>病人出院行唔到樓梯 即係得1條友係咁<br />\n<br />\n哇 真係好得人驚呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得中廢炎會死嘅人<br />\n我唔想反駁你了<br />\n請你唔好出街<br />\n<br />\n覺得廢炎中左會有後遺症嘅<br />\n上面有醫生講嘅數據<br />\n400人得30人有 (個人覺得係廢老先有)<br />\n行唔到樓梯得一個 傳媒就中意拎黎講<br />\n好似 Trump 話: He won .....<br />\n<br />\n一隻病中左可以無病徵<br />\n又可以無啦啦好返<br />\n你話有後遺症? 數據講 好小機會<br />\n發燒都會燒壞腦 <br />\n可能就係燒壞左班恐懼症精神病人嘅腦<br />\n<br />\n搞清自己驚咩未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643ec5c0bd17acb98339591acb34adcae8bb8a5a","tid":2291512,"uid":69650,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"希望你唔會害死左屋企老人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed980097d4969cd0aefb0ee9780f6a146e280ce","tid":2291512,"uid":276273,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"香港醫療係咁，你以為醫好咗咩，<br />\n少年你太年輕，<br />\n你睇沙士個批，成世慘過當年死咗"},{"pid":"1f6e69213a43aa0c7e52ed7d0fe4d8012b8c00cf","tid":2291512,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"643ec5c0bd17acb98339591acb34adcae8bb8a5a","tid":2291512,"uid":69650,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"希望你唔會害死左屋企老人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:14:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚驚就返入老母個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c83feead2ff2a1a7664f29a5684f475cd701f5","tid":2291512,"uid":51790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:16:09.000Z","msg":"得喇得喇<br />\n你出街咪戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1923849957ac4d57105cf7257efdf31582d831","tid":2291512,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:06:50.000Z","msg":"袋定兩千蚊,口罩都唔洗戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d48a9212dfdccfc12f243d025b717ace1da6e2","tid":2291512,"uid":345840,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"就算係400個入面得30<br />\n都有7.5%有後遺症<br />\n你不如搵下有邊D其他傳染病有咁高機率有後遺症先啦<br />\n而且香港死亡率係全球特別低<br />\n自己上網睇下外國宜家仲爆緊爆成點先出黎講啦"},{"pid":"300e6fae2668b0a81581b8eab746d43371b8b594","tid":2291512,"uid":345840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T02:12:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lih